  </div>

  <div id="root"></div>

  <footer>
    <span class="barlbl"><i></i> Data: TheSpaceDevs &middot; Briefing: OpenAI &middot; Alerts: CallMeBot / Discord</span>
    <span>Orchestrated &amp; served entirely by <span class="n8n">n8n</span></span>
  </footer>
